* Reparatur 4.0 / repair 4.0
  IF reguh-koinh EQ space.
    reguh-koinh = reguh-znme1.
  ENDIF.
  IF reguh-pyord NE space.
    reguh-vblnr = reguh-pyord.
  ENDIF.

* Reparatur IBAN / repair IBAN
  call function 'FI_TECH_ACCNO_CHECK_TRY'
    exporting
